data.text: Well you tell me why it's in the testing column. Was I made aware that it was released? Usually from testing I move to ready to release. I know Neil tested  last as he wanted to run through it from beginning to end. It also doesnt look complete, so I was still under the impression it was being tested by Neil and worked on by dev. @stefanbar @yasserogier @lylenutt @willemhuman @lungisaximbi
